    "The main message was that the investments should not be selected by combining multiple individual securities with preferable risk and return characteristics but by determining how they contribute to the overall portfolio.",
    "The efficient frontier concept was formulated based on two distributional measures, namely mean and variance, from which the investor could choose the preferred asset allocation.",
